Dear Rick Buy,

 

INTERNATIONAL TREASURY MANAGEMENT


Tuesday 12 - Thursday 14 March, 2002, Westin Stamford Hotel, Stamford, CT




The early registration deadline is fast approaching - book today and save up to $300!


 


This is the only international treasury event in the US for senior treasury professionals and is your opportunity to join the leaders in cash management from the companies making a difference.


 

PROGRAM HIGHLIGHTS

?         Determine the most appropriate strategy and structure for your international operations 

?         Examine the treasury's role in managing risk exposure on an enterprise-wide basis 

?         Review effective working capital management on a global scale 

?         Discover methodologies for better evaluation of corporate investments 

?         Learn how to use earnings-at-risk methodologies to aggregate risk 

?         Implement a supply chain financing program to improve relationships on the buy and sell-side 

 

Plus! Running concurrently on Thursday March 14th will be a special one day conference devoted to Treasury Management in Emerging Markets - the only conference of its kind running in the US this year. Re-examine your strategy in these regions and to learn how US corporations can survive and thrive. 

 

For full program details and to register, please visit our website www.eurofinance.co.uk. Alternatively, please contact Kendra Bahneman on + 1 212 956 1516 or email kbahneman@eurofinance.co.uk. 

 

In order to qualify for the early registration rate, you must book before February 6, 2002.

 

